    <text>
    <body>
        <p>Residence: Louisville, Jefferson County, Kentucky. A Louisville undertaker since c1833. Born in Shelby County, Kentucky, son of Peter Pearson and Susan Crow. Came to Louisville age 21 (c1831). Married Mary A. Duhurst, of Philadelphia, in 1842.</p>

    </body>
